{"TopicId":197113,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Generate kerbal negative g-load with mod?","CreatedByName":"GKSP","CreatedById":160883,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-25T01:10:23Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"GKSP","CreatedById":160883,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-25T01:10:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen kerbal G-limits are enabled, that applies to any direction, whether positive or negative g.\u00A0 However, pilots (and planes) typically have a much lower g-limit when it comes to negative G.\u00A0 Is there a mod out there that gives kerbals a separate tolerance for negative G so you have to fly aircraft properly?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraktal","CreatedById":184990,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-25T01:21:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think I\u0027ve ever seen negative g in the game in the several years I\u0027ve been playing. Is it even a thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GKSP","CreatedById":160883,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-25T01:23:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223859213\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197113\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221600996866\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184990\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraktal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Fraktal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think I\u0027ve ever seen negative g in the game in the several years I\u0027ve been playing. Is it even a thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNegative G is all relative to direction.\u00A0 It looks like KSP only measures the absolute value of the G-load.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansAcker","CreatedById":195534,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-27T08:08:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf any, I\u0027d expect to see it in this mod but it hasn\u0027t been updated in a few years:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022104207\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4938455551\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/113341-130-122-g-effects-blackouts-redouts-g-locs-v042-2017-jun-25/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-09-27T08:09:11Z\u0022 title=\u002209/27/2020 08:09  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 27, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by HansAcker\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}